metadata.name: Sequoia Haze
metadata.description:
I captured this moment in November while visiting the Sequoia National park in 2017. During its Fall season the scenery was very foggy and eerie in the mountains as you climbed up into the clouds. 
With the purchase of this NFT you will be shipped a 1/1 signed print. You will also be airdropped a 3D photo card in the shape of a film negative. The photo card has. AR/VR capabilities, the usdz file can be projected and you can "hang" the photo via AR anywhere with an iphone.
